data.value:
v1.0.2.5 * 64bit and better DPI handling * Macros can contain comments * Tuning parameters have bigger ranges * Bugfix Closing a serial port was done twice
v1.0.2.4 * You can move macros around by pressing CTRL and then drag and drop to an empty spot
v1.0.2.3 * Missed saving "Initial RTS and DTR" states to disk as well
v1.0.2.2 * Moved FREEZE button to the left margin (on request) and changed it to a button instead of checkbox * Freeze is now triggered on mouse DOWN instead of waiting for the complete click to be processed
v1.0.2.1 * Fixed race condition when closing serial port * small improvements
v1.0.2.0 * Major update. * Fixed a memory leak in v1.0.1.x
v1.0.1.1 * Added "Clear" checkbox. When checked, will clear the command line when ENTER is pressed.
v1.0.1.0 * Added fine-tuning options and history * Added Quick Launch button to start another session without having to close the current connection * Added 'Export' to *.rtf/*.txt option. (.RTF files retain colors information and are opened by Word). * Pressing 'Escape' will close a dialog box * Ability to freeze the display when a specified key word is detected
Beta-13 * Added more baud rate constants
Beta-12 * Increased the Rx and Tx buffer sizes. (It was missing data). * Added feature to set initial RTS and DTR states * Fixed bug when clicking on HISTORY line * Serial and Tx and Rx timeouts added - else it may sit forever waiting on the port * Eliminated the send queue and put straight into send buffer - faster response on sending
